Ferrus Caldwell (Original Character)
Weapon type: Sword
Crystal Color: Yellow
Spheres: A E E

Skill 1: Blast Punch
 Gain BRV based on ATK (50%) before a 1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Becomes Blast Rush when [Ascension] is active.
Blast Rush:
 4-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Uses: 6
15cp: Lumia
 +Greatly increases BRV potency of Blast Punch and Blast Rush
 +Increases BRV gain based of ATK when using Blast Punch (+50%)
 +Grants ATK Up (40%) to self for 6 turns after using Blast Punch or Blast Rush
c.55: Blast Punch Extend
 +Greatly increases BRV gain based on ATK (+100%)
 +Becomes a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
Blast Rush:
 +Becomes a 1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered 5 times
 +Increases own BRV by 20% of total HP damage dealt after each HP attack (excl. last)
 +Allows for 120% Gained BRV overflow
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow

Skill 2: Riptide
 Raises own BRV based on ATK (30%), then multiplies BRV by x1.3.
 Grants [Ascension] to self for 4 turns.
 Becomes Unbound Blade when [Ascension] is active.
 Does not consume skill usage.
Unbound Blade:
 2-hit AoE Melee BRV+ST HP attack.
 Deals 20% splash HP damage to non-targets.
 Delays all targets by 2 turns.
 Inflicts [Banish] on all enemies for 2 turns.
 Uses: 3
35cp: Flamentine
 +Greatly increases BRV gain based on ATK (+50%) when using Riptide
 +Greatly increases BRV potency of Unbound Blade
 +Increases splash HP damage dealt with Unbound Blade (+30%)
 +Extends duration of [Banish] by 2 turns
c.60: Riptide Extend
 +Adds 1 use
 +Increases BRV gain based on ATK (+70%) when using Riptide
 +Triggers a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack after using Riptide
 +Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+ while [Ascension] is active
 +Turns HP Attack to HP Attack+ while [Ascension] is active
Unbound Blade:
 +Tremendously increases BRV potency
 +Becomes a 4-hit AoE Melee BRV+ST HP attack
 +Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow
 
[Ascension]: ATK Up (40%), Max BRV Up (80%)
             HP Regen (20%)
             Thunder Enchant (20%)
[Banish]: INT BRV Down (30%)
          Prevents target from gaining buffs
BRV Attack+: 4-hit Thunder Melee BRV attack
HP Attack+: 3-hit AoE Thunder Melee BRV+ST HP attack
            Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
 
EX: Champion
 +Equips EX ability Fatal Volley
3-hit AoE Ranged Thunder BRV+HP attack.
Deals 100% HP damage to all targets.
Inflicts INT BRV Down (50%) and Sap on all targets for 4 turns.
Inflicts Confusion on all targets for 1 turn.
Grants [Daring Duelist] to self for 3 turns.
 Recast: Slightly Slow
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases recast speed of Fatal Volley by 20%
  -LB3: Extends duration of [Daring Duelist] by 3 turns
 EX+: Combines INT BRV Down and Sap into [Hollow Curse], and extends its duration by 2 turns
      Grants [Ascension] to self for 4 turns after use
  -LB1: Raises own ATK (40%) and Max BRV (60%)
  -LB2: At Quest Start:
        Grants [Daring Duelist] and ATK Up (50%) to self for 6 turns
        Fills Recast Gauge to 70%
  -LB3: Becomes a 6-hit AoE Thunder Ranged BRV+HP attack
        Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
        If [Ascension] is active, resets all targets' BREAK status before BRV hits
        Turns BRV Attack, BRV Attack+ to Shock when [Ascension] is active
        Turns HP Attack, HP Attack+ to Dynamo when [Ascension] is active

[Daring Duelist]: INT BRV Up (150%), Max BRV Up (50%)
                  Raises own ATK based on number of enemies present (30%/60%/90%)
                  BRV Regen, effect up based on number of enemies present (50%/100%/150% iBRV)
[Hollow Curse]: INT BRV Down (50%), Max BRV Down (50%), Sap
                Thunder Resistance Down
Shock: 3-hit AoE Thunder Melee BRV attack.
       Dispels 1 buff on all targets when Breaking/attacking a Broken target
Dynamo: 2-hit Thunder Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered twice.

